In an interview with #TNIE, Industries Minister @TRBRajaa highlighted that the #TamilNau government is stepping up efforts to bolster infrastructure in its southern districts to keep #VOCPort competitive over the long term and will soon unveil a warehousing policy and adopt a long-term strategic plan aimed at reinforcing its logistics backbone.

